def test_diff_ranges(self) -> None:
        a = ["hello", "world"]
        b = ["hello", "world"]

        assert diff_ranges(a, b) == (
            [(0, 0), (0, 2), (2, 2), (2, 2)],
            [(0, 0), (0, 2), (2, 2), (2, 2)],
        )

        a = ["hello", "world"]
        b = ["goodbye", "world"]

        assert diff_ranges(a, b) == (
            [(0, 1), (1, 2), (2, 2), (2, 2)],
            [(0, 1), (1, 2), (2, 2), (2, 2)],
        )
